{{codepointer|Sound}}
'''{{class|StateProvider}}'''

{{c|action void '''A_FireBFG'''()}}
{{superseded|A_StartSound}}

==Usage==
Plays the sound "weapons/bfgf".

== Examples ==
This is taken directly from the {{Class|BFG9000}}.
<syntaxhighlight lang="csharp">
	Fire:
		BFGG A 20 A_BFGsound;
		BFGG B 10 A_GunFlash;
		BFGG B 10 A_FireBFG;
		BFGG B 20 A_ReFire;
		Goto Ready;
</syntaxhighlight>

==[[ZScript]] definition==
{{ZScriptDefinitionNote|actors/doom/weaponbfg.zs}} 
<syntaxhighlight lang="csharp">
	action void A_BFGsound() 
	{ 
		A_StartSound("weapons/bfgf", CHAN_WEAPON); 
	}</syntaxhighlight>

